he'll definitely want you to be his supportive wife.

4
00:02:06,199 --> 00:02:07,680
All those promises he made before

5
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,919
were just a momentary impulse.

6
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,559
They won't last long.

7
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,639
Women are naturally just men's appendages.

8
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:19,160
Besides, your family works as coroners, which is an unconventional trade.

9
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:21,919
Dealing with corpses isn't considered a proper profession.

10
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,440
Women should stay at home,

11
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:25,679
serve their husbands, and be filial to their in-laws.

12
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:28,279
The world outside the home belongs to men.

13
00:02:28,839 --> 00:02:30,559
I didn't know there were female coroners.

14
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,600
