16
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,639
Here in Gushan,

17
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:38,440
even though people don't steal and doors are left unlocked at night,

18
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,639
you have no cases to investigate.

19
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:40,520
But

20
00:02:40,839 --> 00:02:42,919
you can help me manage Gushan.

21
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,320
