22
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,160
Linlang,

23
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,440
let me tell you,

24
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,520
men will never see

25
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,039
the sacrifices we make for them.

26
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,759
Women should live for themselves.

27
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,960
Right now, I only care about the academy.

28
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,800
I'm leaving now.

29
00:02:55,839 --> 00:02:57,320
Don't go!

30
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,279
You...

31
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,479
What's wrong?

32
00:03:01,119 --> 00:03:02,479
I'm fine.

33
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,279
I just feel a little unwell.

34
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,440
I'm going out for some air.

35
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:07,880
Jiu'er,

36
00:03:10,679 --> 00:03:11,919
