37
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,160
As the dean, it's improper for you to leave your guests.

38
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,240
You're no longer

39
00:03:15,279 --> 00:03:16,600
someone who acts alone.

40
00:03:16,679 --> 00:03:18,559
You need to consider everyone in Gushan.

41
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,440
Go.

42
00:03:25,559 --> 00:03:26,240
Go back.

43
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:07,520
From now on, the academy will rely on all of you.

44
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,320
Young Master Lu, let me offer you a toast.

45
00:04:30,799 --> 00:04:31,720
Lord Geng.

46
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:47,760
