113
00:07:05,799 --> 00:07:08,040
Staying here is the best way you can help him

114
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,480
Come

115
00:07:22,679 --> 00:07:24,640
This time, it was thanks to the young chief's brilliant strategy

116
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,320
that we were able to repel those soldiers

117
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,640
Yes, that's right

