134
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:13,720
You have gone from pretending to be a wealthy young man

135
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:16,160
to becoming the respected young hero of Gushan

136
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,440
You have found your own path in life

137
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,519
Then I

138
00:08:20,239 --> 00:08:22,119
should also go find mine

139
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,399
