152
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:25,840
I don't know who it was just now,

153
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:27,359
but the way you looked at Sima Kong,

154
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,359
was so intense.

155
00:09:28,719 --> 00:09:30,000
But you are the Young Chieftain.

156
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,400
Of course you have to be more restrained than I am.

157
00:09:31,479 --> 00:09:32,840
If you want me to restrain myself, that's fine.

158
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:33,840
You...

159
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,119
Help me find something.

160
00:09:36,119 --> 00:09:37,000
Something?

161
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,599
Linlang.

162
00:10:02,359 --> 00:10:03,200
Where are you going?

163
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,599
Linlang is gone.

164
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,239
How could that be?

165
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,200
Linlang has been feeling down lately.

166
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,239
