172
00:10:18,359 --> 00:10:19,919
is to find Miss Xu's whereabouts.

173
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,320
The footprints from the table to the door

174
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,760
judging by their size and depth,

175
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:28,719
match Miss Xu's build.

176
00:10:29,599 --> 00:10:31,320
She must have entered the room not long ago,

177
00:10:31,599 --> 00:10:32,719
saw this letter,

178
00:10:33,119 --> 00:10:33,960
then suddenly turned around

179
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:34,679
and left the room.

180
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,239
What could be in that letter?

181
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,080
The content isn't important.

182
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,200
The person who left the message

183
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,400
entered the room through this window.

184
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,359
He was very careful.

185
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,280
Before leaving,

186
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,880
he erased any traces he left behind.

187
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,159
But precisely

188
00:10:53,359 --> 00:10:55,000
the traces that were different from elsewhere

189
00:10:55,119 --> 00:10:56,239
revealed his movements.

190
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,719
The scent of kaolin.

191
00:11:07,119 --> 00:11:08,919
Kaolin is only found at Phoenix Mountain.

192
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,559
Linlang must have gone there.

193
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:11,760
Phoenix Mountain.

194
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:13,440
It's guarded by the sentries of Lone Mountain.

195
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,239
Once caught, it's hard to escape.

196
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,039
They would never walk into a trap.

197
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,239
You mean

198
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,239
Longchi Cliff.

199
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,520
I've seen the defense map of Lone Mountain.

200
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,239
There,

201
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,840
is only a few miles from Phoenix Mountain.

202
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,919
It's located in Mist Town.

203
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,280
Between it and Lone Mountain,

204
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,039
the terrain is treacherous, easy to defend and hard to attack.

205
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,799
There's also a shortcut

206
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,520
that allows for a secret escape.

207
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,520
That person took Linlang there.

208
00:11:34,719 --> 00:11:35,559
Could it be

209
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:45,039
No wonder you were once with the authorities.

210
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:46,440
You're very punctual.

211
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:47,599
Uncle.

212
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,520
Your father and I were both former members of Fenglei Hall.

213
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:58,159
You can call me uncle.

214
00:11:58,239 --> 00:11:59,479
That would be appropriate.

215
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:01,719
My father was a member of Fenglei Hall.

216
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,280
It seems that for the past twenty years,

217
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,039
your father truly kept silent.

218
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,400
He even hid it from his own daughter.

219
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,799
If he hadn't killed Tianluo,

220
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,840
the assassin hunting down the remnants of Fenglei Hall,

221
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,559
no one in this world would know his true identity.

222
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,880
You even know about this.

223
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:16,960
Who are you, really?

224
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,559
Miss, don't be afraid.

225
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:25,599
Since you've saved my son Lu Jiu many times,

226
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,440
I won't harm you.

227
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:29,280
Your son?

228
00:12:29,479 --> 00:12:30,479
You are Lu Kun.

229
00:12:35,479 --> 00:12:36,960
Tang Sect's hidden weapons.

230
00:12:47,119 --> 00:12:48,760
I know you want to use me to threaten Lu Jiu.

231
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:49,799
Dream on.

232
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,559
Father.

233
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:17,000
You haven't wanted to see me for years.

234
00:13:17,599 --> 00:13:18,599
I never expected

235
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,599
we would meet like this.

236
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:24,919
You still remember I'm your father.

237
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,919
I thought after you reunited with your mother,

238
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,919
you would cut all ties with me.

239
00:13:29,359 --> 00:13:30,799
Even though you've done many wrongs,

240
00:13:31,799 --> 00:13:33,520
the years you raised me,

241
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:35,440
I, Lu Jiu, dare not forget.

242
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:37,119
But you've forgotten the most important thing.

243
00:13:43,719 --> 00:13:44,599
Lu Jiu.

244
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:56,640
I had no other choice, my son.

245
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,719
I placed you by Tianluo's side

246
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,919
at least so you could stay alive.

247
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:02,159
Otherwise, both of us would have died long ago.

248
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:04,200
All my efforts and intentions

249
00:14:05,359 --> 00:14:06,559
do you understand them?

250
00:14:08,479 --> 00:14:09,359
Now,

251
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,760
you've already found the whereabouts of the treasure.

252
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,359
We can now

253
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,119
break free from Tianluo's control.

254
00:14:15,159 --> 00:14:16,960
You and I can share the treasure together.

255
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:20,320
I can even give you a warm home.

256
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,640
Come.

257
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,039
You are my father.

258
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,080
