00:16:05,679 --> 00:16:07,520
Though you barely survived

284
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,679
You lost your memory and wandered the streets

285
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:11,719
I took you in and raised you

286
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,159
Otherwise, you wouldn’t be here today

287
00:16:13,599 --> 00:16:14,440
Father

288
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:18,520
