291
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,640
Why bring up the past

292
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,599
Better to think about the present

293
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:33,919
We, father and son, could share the treasure and rule the world

294
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,119
How joyful that would be

295
00:16:36,479 --> 00:16:37,799
Give me the treasure

296
00:16:39,119 --> 00:16:41,119
We could go back to how things were

297
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:42,479
Yes

298
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,760
Just like before

299
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,880
You kept me

300
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,440
No, imprisoned me

301
00:16:54,239 --> 00:16:56,320
You imprisoned me in Luoyang County

302
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:58,640
Waiting for the day you could use me

303
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,960
Lu Kun

304
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:04,800
Today

305
00:17:05,239 --> 00:17:06,640
The two of us

306
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:10,000
Let’s end our father-son relationship here

307
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:16,839
Sure.

308
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:18,599
Then let me see what you've got.

309
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,319
Show me what you're capable of.

310
00:17:24,959 --> 00:17:25,839
Are you scared?

311
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,400
I'm not scared.

312
00:17:29,319 --> 00:17:30,520
When I'm with you,

313
00:17:31,079 --> 00:17:32,560
even if the sky falls, I'm not afraid.

314
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:46,319
Do you still remember

315
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,319
seven years ago,

316
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:51,160
how I got my revenge on you?

317
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,719
No, don't.

318
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,319
Linlang, you're awake.

319
00:18:35,599 --> 00:18:36,680
How did I get back?

320
00:18:36,719 --> 00:18:37,959
Lu Jiu brought you back.

321
00:18:41,439 --> 00:18:42,599
Where is he?

322
00:18:44,359 --> 00:18:45,160
He...

323
00:18:46,839 --> 00:18:47,959
How is he?

324
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:51,160
Why does this child always make people worry?

325
00:18:55,119 --> 00:18:56,239
Did Lu Jiu really do it for me?

326
00:18:56,319 --> 00:18:57,520
Did something bad happen to him?

327
