Stop talking.

328
00:18:59,319 --> 00:19:00,199
Stop talking.

329
00:19:02,239 --> 00:19:03,959
Lu Jiu is such a fool.

330
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:08,319
Is that how you talk about your savior?

331
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,599
You're not dead?

332
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:13,479
Who said I was dead?

333
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,959
I just hadn't finished speaking earlier.

334
00:19:19,199 --> 00:19:20,640
What exactly happened?

335
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:21,560
I remember

336
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,359
the two of us fell off the cliff together.

337
00:19:23,479 --> 00:19:24,920
After that, I passed out.

338
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,560
And then,

339
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,760
you fell into the trap I had set up in advance.

340
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,880
Lu Jiu and I are clever,

341
00:19:30,959 --> 00:19:32,839
how could we go to save someone without being prepared?

342
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:37,719
No wonder you jumped down without hesitation.

343
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,280
But

344
00:19:39,479 --> 00:19:41,239
how did Chief Xu end up like this?

345
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:43,680
I just got a minor injury.

346
00:19:43,719 --> 00:19:45,000
Mother was especially worried.

347
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:46,920
So she had someone bandage me up like this.

348
00:19:47,239 --> 00:19:48,640
You should understand the chief.

349
00:19:48,839 --> 00:19:49,640
As a mother,

350
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:51,439
she can't bear to see her son hurt at all.

351
00:19:51,479 --> 00:19:52,920
Mother, don't worry.

352
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,000
It's all bandaged up.

353
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,719
See, I'm fine.

354
00:19:56,319 --> 00:19:57,599
How can you say you're fine?

355
00:20:00,119 --> 00:20:02,920
According to Gushan custom, you shouldn't get married if you're injured.

356
00:20:03,439 --> 00:20:04,800
So your wedding with Linlang

357
00:20:04,839 --> 00:20:06,280
will have to be postponed again.

358
00:20:06,959 --> 00:20:09,119
When will I finally get to hold my grandson?

359
00:20:09,239 --> 00:20:11,119
Linlang and I won't be getting married for now.

360
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:31,160
Linlang and I won't be getting married for now.

361
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:41,000
It's so spicy, it's killing me!

362
00:20:41,959 --> 00:20:43,800
Why does this wine taste so bad?

363
00:20:44,359 --> 00:20:45,239
Wine.

364
00:20:46,239 --> 00:20:47,800
It's not about the taste of the drink.

365
00:20:48,479 --> 00:20:49,800
Then what are you drinking for?

366
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:51,640
It's the sorrow in the wine.

367
00:20:51,959 --> 00:20:53,000
The heartbreak of those parted.

368
00:20:54,239 --> 00:20:56,239
They say one drunken night can ease a thousand worries.

369
00:20:56,839 --> 00:20:58,280
What troubles you, sir?

370
00:21:06,319 --> 00:21:07,439
I'm returning to the capital.

371
00:21:07,479 --> 00:21:08,599
To find Bai Yu.

372
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:10,599
It has nothing to do with her.

373
00:21:11,079 --> 00:21:12,520
I was ordered to eliminate Gushan.

374
00:21:13,079 --> 00:21:14,160
But I switched sides at the last moment.

375
00:21:14,439 --> 00:21:15,280
I must go back.

376
00:21:15,599 --> 00:21:16,520
To give an explanation.

377
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:18,319
Now the court is in chaos because of Wuxiang City.

378
00:21:18,359 --> 00:21:19,680
It's all a mess.

379
00:21:20,319 --> 00:21:22,920
This time, you saved the people of Gushan—

380
00:21:23,119 --> 00:21:24,280
I saved the people of Gushan

381
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,400
out of righteousness.

382
00:21:26,079 --> 00:21:27,760
Returning to the capital to report and accept punishment

383
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:28,920
is out of loyalty.

384
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:31,239
These are the principles I, Geng Zhao, pursue.

385
00:21:31,439 --> 00:21:32,239
What must be faced

386
00:21:32,439 --> 00:21:33,319
will have to be faced eventually.

387
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,640
Master Geng, your integrity is admirable.

388
00:21:36,959 --> 00:21:37,959
Linlang is impressed.

389
00:21:38,479 --> 00:21:40,359
In the past, I saw you as my goal.

390
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,520
From now on, you are even more my role model.

391
00:21:44,479 --> 00:21:45,400
Since you've given me such praise,

392
00:21:45,479 --> 00:21:46,719
I have to live up to it.

393
00:21:47,079 --> 00:21:48,000
There's something

394
00:21:48,239 --> 00:21:49,439
I must give you.

395
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:56,839
Here.

396
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:02,119
This is the selection approval document for the Diancha Department.

397
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:03,520
I can take the Diancha Department exam now.

398
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:04,439
The Diancha Department is recruiting.

399
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:05,560
Although there are no gender restrictions,

400
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:07,280
over the past few decades,

401
00:22:07,439 --> 00:22:09,199
very few women have been selected.

402
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,479
Even if they are selected,

403
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,040
most are royal relatives or nobles.

404
00:22:12,119 --> 00:22:13,160
They do it just for fun.

405
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:18,479
The Diancha Department has always had strict requirements for hiring women.

406
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,239
But fortunately, my father is a prince.

407
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:21,599
As long as I'm interested in handling cases,

408
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,839
no one dares to stop me.

409
00:22:24,160 --> 00:22:25,359
Interested in handling cases,

410
00:22:26,119 --> 00:22:27,760
but I'm even more interested in you.

411
00:22:28,839 --> 00:22:29,599
Sir,

412
00:22:32,959 --> 00:22:34,640
don't think this is a life-saving charm.

413
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,000
You still have to pass the exam

414
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,719
to truly enter the Diancha Department.

415
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,000
Linlang understands.

416
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,640
But do you understand, sir?

417
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:43,760
Understand what?

418
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:45,239
You know what I'm talking about.

419
00:22:45,319 --> 00:22:46,959
For people who share the same feelings,

420
00:22:47,439 --> 00:22:49,280
if they keep everything in their hearts,

421
00:22:49,359 --> 00:22:50,800
they will only grow further apart.

422
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:53,959
What a coincidence.

423
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:56,359
Someone else said the same thing.

424
00:22:56,839 --> 00:22:57,959
Who was it?

425
00:22:58,479 --> 00:22:59,560
Someone who asked me to help you get

426
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,479
the Diancha Department selection qualification.

427
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,719
I hope you will grant this request.

428
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:17,479
Miss Xu's skills in autopsy and investigation

429
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,760
have long met the standards of the Diancha Department.

430
00:23:20,119 --> 00:23:22,239
I have often wanted to recruit her under my command.

431
00:23:22,439 --> 00:23:23,359
But regarding this matter,

432
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:24,959
why didn't Miss Xu come to me herself?

433
00:23:25,319 --> 00:23:26,599
His Majesty governs the country

434
00:23:26,839 --> 00:23:28,000
with an emphasis on checks and balances.

435
00:23:28,359 --> 00:23:29,719
The Tianluo mercenaries maintain their own authority,

436
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,560
so there is an intention to support the Diancha Department.

437
00:23:31,760 --> 00:23:32,920
Furthermore, it is stipulated

438
00:23:33,599 --> 00:23:35,560
that among the three Tianluo clans,

439
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:37,000
no death warrior may enter the Diancha Department.

440
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:40,719
Although you now go by the name Lu Jiu,

441
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,839
on your official records,

442
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:44,680
you are still registered as Fei Ying, a Tianluo death warrior.

443
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,800
Are you worried that your relationship with her

444
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,319
will affect her career?

445
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:49,800
No.

446
00:23:50,479 --> 00:23:51,520
For the Diancha Department,

447
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,280
to Linlang,

448
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:55,319
it is not about rank or official position,

449
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:56,599
but about her dream.

450
00:23:57,599 --> 00:23:59,119
I want to help her fulfill her dream.

451
00:24:00,239 --> 00:24:02,160
Miss Xu is determined to pursue justice in criminal cases,

452
00:24:02,479 --> 00:24:03,959
upholding a heart of fairness.

453
00:24:04,359 --> 00:24:05,640
Now you ask me

454
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,959
to make an exception and secure her selection.

455
00:24:08,319 --> 00:24:10,239
Wouldn't that tarnish her aspirations?

456
00:24:10,359 --> 00:24:11,319
The Diancha Department

457
00:24:11,479 --> 00:24:12,680
can treat Linlang fairly.

458
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:13,719
With Linlang's abilities,

459
00:24:13,760 --> 00:24:15,079
I believe she can enter

460
00:24:15,119 --> 00:24:16,119
the Diancha Department honorably.

461
00:24:17,719 --> 00:24:18,719
As for me,

462
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,119
I am willing to remain unmarried for life

463
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:30,239
to help her achieve her wish.

464
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,079
Why are you here?

465
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:48,959
You—

466
00:24:50,479 --> 00:24:53,239
Is it because of what happened with my mother and me today—

467
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,000
Idiot.

468
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,959
Who said you could make decisions on your own?

469
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:06,880
Lord Geng,

470
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:10,439
you usually seem so quiet and reserved,

471
00:25:11,079 --> 00:25:12,760
but you can't even keep something like this a secret.

472
00:25:14,359 --> 00:25:16,359
I just want to ask you one thing right now.

473
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,319
Do you want to marry me?

474
00:25:25,599 --> 00:25:26,959
Of course I do.

475
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,800
Then let's get married in the spring.

476
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:32,920
Ah—

477
00:25:33,319 --> 00:25:35,119
Even though my father has passed away,

478
00:25:35,479 --> 00:25:37,119
the betrothal gifts, the engagement, the formal proposal—

479
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,079
the name inquiry, the setting of the date—

480
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,359
not a single step can be skipped.

481
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,920
I don't want my father to come to me in a dream and ask

482
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,760
