483
00:25:44,199 --> 00:25:45,160
But—

484
00:25:46,319 --> 00:25:48,760
Haven't you always wanted to join the Diancha Office?

485
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:55,800
The Diancha Office was my dream in the past.

486
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:57,959
But you

487
00:25:58,839 --> 00:26:01,599
are my dream now and in the future.

488
00:26:07,439 --> 00:26:08,959
There's one more thing.

489
00:26:10,079 --> 00:26:12,560
From now on, you're not allowed to hide anything from me.

490
00:26:14,959 --> 00:26:15,680
Okay.

491
00:26:18,079 --> 00:26:19,599
And one more thing—

492
00:26:29,079 --> 00:26:30,000
This

493
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:33,119
This is

494
00:26:34,119 --> 00:26:35,640
When I first came to Gushan

495
00:26:36,319 --> 00:26:38,119
I saw how you felt about that set of dissection tools

496
00:26:38,199 --> 00:26:39,400
You were unwilling to accept it

497
00:26:40,959 --> 00:26:42,160
After thinking it over

498
00:26:42,280 --> 00:26:44,479
I made a set for you myself

499
00:26:46,199 --> 00:26:47,920
You made this yourself?

500
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:49,839
Yes

501
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:52,359
I’ve never done this kind of handiwork before

502
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,199
