503
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:55,560
But

504
00:26:56,479 --> 00:26:57,959
Isn’t this just like how you investigate cases

505
00:26:58,280 --> 00:26:59,640
Slowly searching for the truth

506
00:27:02,839 --> 00:27:04,040
You’re always like this

507
00:27:04,479 --> 00:27:06,199
Quietly doing so much for me

