511
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:22,319
I just hope

512
00:27:23,719 --> 00:27:25,319
You’ll always be happy

513
00:28:12,439 --> 00:28:13,359
The left side is one inch higher.

514
00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:15,239
That's not right.

515
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,680
You're two inches higher.

516
00:28:17,319 --> 00:28:18,160
Young Master Sima,

517
00:28:18,199 --> 00:28:19,640
