521
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:24,920
The right side is half an inch lower.

522
00:28:26,199 --> 00:28:26,640
That's too much.

523
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:27,800
Raise it a bit.

524
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:29,319
That's right.

525
00:28:30,359 --> 00:28:31,599
It seems giving you this task

526
00:28:31,719 --> 00:28:32,880
was the right choice.

527
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,680
If you had stuck to the original plan and married in spring,

528
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:36,959
I could have prepared even better.

529
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:39,119
But you suddenly decided to get married before the New Year.

530
00:28:39,199 --> 00:28:40,760
Now I'm caught off guard.

531
00:28:41,439 --> 00:28:42,239
Linlang and I

532
00:28:42,319 --> 00:28:43,959
have finally made it to this day.

533
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,160
If we don't get married for one more day,

534
00:28:45,439 --> 00:28:46,800
I'll be uneasy for another day.

535
00:28:47,359 --> 00:28:49,000
Sorry to trouble you, Young Master Sima.

536
00:28:49,160 --> 00:28:50,520
Please bear with me.

537
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:51,719
Don't try to get close to me.

538
00:28:52,119 --> 00:28:53,560
