00:28:59,959 --> 00:29:01,439
if you add up all the expenses,

544
00:29:01,479 --> 00:29:02,800
about Miss Xing'er,

545
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:05,560
that was just an act for Linlang, wasn't it?

546
00:29:08,479 --> 00:29:09,800
The day Linlang disappeared

547
00:29:10,479 --> 00:29:11,400
Your reaction

548
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:12,640
can't fool anyone

549
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,400
You won't tell Linlang, right?

550
00:29:15,439 --> 00:29:16,760
