00:29:41,239 --> 00:29:43,199
Actually, our goals are the same

562
00:29:44,119 --> 00:29:45,160
As long as Linlang is happy

563
00:29:47,199 --> 00:29:48,520
I hope you won't let her down

564
00:29:49,199 --> 00:29:51,199
And don't let down the compromise I've made for you

565
00:29:54,479 --> 00:29:55,199
Mm

566
00:30:11,319 --> 00:30:12,359
The wedding date is approaching quickly.

567
00:30:12,439 --> 00:30:14,800
I thought we'd have to rush the tailor to make alterations.

568
00:30:14,959 --> 00:30:16,880
But now it seems to fit perfectly.

569
00:30:16,959 --> 00:30:18,160
No further changes are needed.

570
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:20,439
This wedding dress is truly beautiful.

571
00:30:20,479 --> 00:30:21,760
It's my first time seeing one.

572
00:30:22,199 --> 00:30:23,040
Miss Xu, before this,

573
00:30:23,119 --> 00:30:25,199
have you never seen anyone else get married?

574
00:30:25,319 --> 00:30:26,280
We're coroners.

575
00:30:26,319 --> 00:30:28,040
Others think we're unlucky.

576
00:30:28,199 --> 00:30:29,280
Whenever there's a happy occasion,

577
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:31,079
they drive us far away.

578
00:30:31,760 --> 00:30:34,199
I'm sure you've heard some gossip too, Miss Xu.

579
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:36,520
They say you only want to work at the Investigation Bureau.

580
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:38,079
That you don't want to be a wife and mother.

581
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,520
And that you're not worthy of the young master.

582
00:30:40,439 --> 00:30:42,640
But seeing you in this wedding dress now,

583
00:30:42,719 --> 00:30:45,119
makes me think it's the young master who's not worthy of you.

584
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:47,079
You're really straightforward.

585
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:49,160
Aren't you afraid I'll be upset by what you say?

586
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,160
Why?

587
00:30:50,319 --> 00:30:52,040
Would you rather I lied to make you happy?

588
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:54,520
You and Sima Kong really are

589
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:56,599
cut from the same cloth.

590
00:30:58,040 --> 00:30:58,880
Miss Xu,

591
00:30:59,000 --> 00:30:59,920
before the wedding,

592
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:02,000
let me teach you some etiquette.

593
00:31:02,439 --> 00:31:03,160
For example,

594
00:31:03,239 --> 00:31:05,719
the last two steps you took were a bit too big.

595
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:08,119
The proper way to walk should be like this.

596
00:31:08,239 --> 00:31:09,479
Keep your shoulders level and steady.

597
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:12,520
Your toes and heels should always be in a straight line.

598
00:31:12,599 --> 00:31:13,800
Just like this.

599
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:15,800
See?

600
00:31:21,479 --> 00:31:22,359
How is it?

601
00:31:22,719 --> 00:31:24,040
I'm used to being casual.

602
00:31:24,119 --> 00:31:25,760
I've never paid attention to these manners.

603
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:27,959
Miss Xu,

604
00:31:28,439 --> 00:31:30,839
Although the people of Gushan are from the martial world,

605
00:31:30,959 --> 00:31:33,439
Master Xu comes from a scholarly family.

606
00:31:33,520 --> 00:31:35,400
She is quite particular about these etiquettes.

607
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,880
She has already sent someone to invite your uncle to attend the ceremony.

608
00:31:37,959 --> 00:31:39,479
She must value this very much.

609
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:41,760
You need to practice more.

610
00:31:44,479 --> 00:31:45,680
Master Xu,

611
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:47,479
Will she not like me?

612
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:49,560
No, she won't. Don't worry.

613
00:31:54,640 --> 00:31:55,760
Master Xu,

614
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:02,599
Who wouldn't like such a beautiful daughter-in-law?

615
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,520
These earrings,

616
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:13,160
were given to me when I first joined Fenglei Hall.

617
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:15,199
They were a welcome gift from the Hall Master's wife.

618
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:17,959
I thought, since you'll continue working as a coroner,

619
00:32:18,119 --> 00:32:19,880
things like jade bracelets or rings

620
00:32:19,959 --> 00:32:21,680
would get in the way of your work.

621
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:23,520
But these suit you perfectly.

622
00:32:24,479 --> 00:32:26,160
Such a precious gift...

623
00:32:27,560 --> 00:32:29,719
In the first half of my life, I met the wrong people.

624
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:32,599
Now, seeing my son marry the one he loves,

625
00:32:33,439 --> 00:32:36,160
I truly feel happy for you both from the bottom of my heart.

626
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,199
Thank you, Chief Xu.

627
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:42,040
These earrings have a peony design.

628
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:44,439
Peonies symbolize a match made in heaven.

629
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:46,119
They are both a flower and a medicine.

630
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,160
Giving them to you now

631
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,920
couldn't be more fitting.

632
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:52,520
What a coincidence,

633
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:54,439
my mother also left me a hairpin

634
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,079
with the same peony design.

635
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:57,800
Linlang.

636
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:01,880
Stop calling, stop calling.

637
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:04,359
It's bad luck for the bride and groom to meet before the wedding.

638
00:33:04,959 --> 00:33:07,520
You two really can't wait, can you?

639
00:33:08,239 --> 00:33:09,680
Chief Xu.

640
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:10,680
Young Chief.

641
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:11,880
Chief Xu's orders.

642
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,839
You can't see each other before the wedding.

643
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,199
Forgive me.

644
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:16,640
Excuse me, Young Chief.

645
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:17,800
Why are you pulling me?

646
00:33:17,959 --> 00:33:18,719
Me?

647
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:21,239
I'll let you call me Chief Xu for two more days.

648
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:23,560
After that, you'll have to change what you call me.
